headline: CNA Canada Appoints Catherine Roe as President
summary: CNA Canada is pleased to announce the appointment of Catherine Roe as President, effective November 10, 2025. Catherine brings more than 30 years of leadership experience in insurance and risk management across North America, most recently serving as Executive Vice President and Central Regional Leader at Aon. Her track record of driving strategic growth and operational excellence with proven market expertise positions her to lead CNA Canada into its next era of innovation and growth.
